OBUISEL_SELECTOR.NAME: Financial Account Form Selector Reference
OBUISEL_SELECTOR.HQL: select e.id as id, e.name || ' - ' || c.iSOCode as completename from FIN_Financial_Account e inner join e.currency as c where @additional_filters@ and e.active=true

OBUISEL_SELECTOR.NAME: Costcenter Form Selector Reference
OBUISEL_SELECTOR.HQL: select e.id as id, e.searchKey || ' - ' || e.name as completename from Costcenter e where @additional_filters@ and e.active=true

OBUISEL_SELECTOR.NAME: Product Form Selector Reference
OBUISEL_SELECTOR.HQL: select e.id as id, e.searchKey || ' - ' || coalesce(scrInternalcode,'-') || ' - ' || e.name as completename from Product e where @additional_filters@ and e.active=true

OBUISEL_SELECTOR.NAME: Product Line Form Selector Reference
OBUISEL_SELECTOR.HQL: select e.id as id, e.searchKey || ' - ' || e.description as completename from PRDC_PRODUCTGROUP e where @additional_filters@ and e.active=true

OBUISEL_SELECTOR.NAME: Payment Method Form Selector Reference
OBUISEL_SELECTOR.HQL: select e.id as id, e.name as completename from FIN_PaymentMethod e where @additional_filters@ and e.active=true

OBUISEL_SELECTOR.NAME: Year Form Selector Reference
OBUISEL_SELECTOR.HQL: select e.id as id, e.fiscalYear as completename from FinancialMgmtYear e where @additional_filters@ and e.active=true

OBUISEL_SELECTOR.NAME: Purchase Price List Form Selector Reference
Bank Financial Accounts Selector Reference
OBUISEL_SELECTOR.HQL: select e.id as id, e.genericAccountNo || ' - ' || coalesce(e.currency.iSOCode,'--') as completename from FIN_Financial_Account e where @additional_filters@ and e.type='B' and coalesce(e.scoForapppayment,'N')='N' and e.active=true

OBUISEL_SELECTOR.NAME: Product with PriceList
OBUISEL_SELECTOR.FILTER_EXPRESSION: "exists(from PricingProductPrice pp where pp.product.id = e.id and pp.priceListVersion.active = \'Y\' and pp.priceListVersion.priceList.id = \'" + OB.getParameters().get('inpmPricelistId') + "\' ) and ((COALESCE(@EM_Ssa_Isserviceorder@,\'\') = \'Y\' and e.productType = \'S\') OR (COALESCE(@EM_Ssa_Isserviceorder@,\'\') <> \'Y\'))"

OBUISEL_SELECTOR.NAME: scr_updatetaxmotive
OBUISEL_SELECTOR.FILTER_EXPRESSION: if (OB.getParameters().get('inpissotrx')=="false" && OB.getParameters().get('inpemScrSpecialtax')=="SCOEXEMPT") {" e.comboCategory.searchKey=\'docCompraTaxExcento\' "} else if (OB.getParameters().get('inpissotrx')=="false" && OB.getParameters().get('inpemScrSpecialtax')=="SCOIGV") {" e.comboCategory.searchKey=\'docCompraTaxIGV\' "} else if (OB.getParameters().get('inpissotrx')=="true" && OB.getParameters().get('inpemScrSpecialtax')=="SCOEXEMPT") {" e.comboCategory.searchKey=\'docVentaTaxExcento\' "} else {"e.comboCategory.searchKey=\'\'"}
OBUISEL_SELECTOR.HQL: select e.id as id, e.searchKey, e.name as cmbname, e.sequenceNumber as sequenceNumber from SCR_Combo_Item e where @additional_filters@

OBUISEL_SELECTOR.NAME: Element Value Form Selector Reference
OBUISEL_SELECTOR.HQL: select e.id as id, e.searchKey || ' - ' || e.name as completename from FinancialMgmtElementValue e where @additional_filters@ and e.elementLevel='S' and e.active=true

OBUISEL_SELECTOR.NAME: BP Document Form Selector Reference
OBUISEL_SELECTOR.HQL: select e.id as id, e.name as completename from SCR_Combo_Item e where @additional_filters@ and e.active=true and e.comboCategory.searchKey='Tipo de Documento de Identidad'

OBUISEL_SELECTOR.NAME: Organization Form Selector Reference
OBUISEL_SELECTOR.HQL: select e.id as id, e.name as completename from Organization e where @additional_filters@ and e.active=true

OBUISEL_SELECTOR.NAME: GLItem Form Selector Reference
OBUISEL_SELECTOR.HQL: select e.id as id, e.name as completename from FinancialMgmtGLItem e where @additional_filters@ and e.active=true

OBUISEL_SELECTOR.NAME: SCR_PhyDocSequence_User_Ref
OBUISEL_SELECTOR.HQL: select e.id as id, e.name || ' - ' || e.prefix as completename from BILL_PhyDocSequence e where @additional_filters_notorg@ and e.active=true

OBUISEL_SELECTOR.NAME: Warehouse Form Selector Reference
OBUISEL_SELECTOR.HQL: select e.id as id, e.searchKey || ' - ' || e.name as completename from Warehouse e where @additional_filters@ and e.active=true

OBUISEL_SELECTOR.NAME: Purchase Invoice DocType Selector
OBUISEL_SELECTOR.HQL: select e.id as id, e.name as completename from SCR_Combo_Item e where @additional_filters@ and e.comboCategory.searchKey='tablasunat10' and e.active=true

OBUISEL_SELECTOR.NAME: Business Partner Form Selector Reference
OBUISEL_SELECTOR.HQL: select e.id as id, coalesce(e.taxID,'') || ' - ' || e.name as completename from BusinessPartner e where @additional_filters@ and e.active=true and e.scrIstemplate=false

OBUISEL_SELECTOR.NAME: SCR_Warehouse_DocTypeSeq_SelRef
OBUISEL_SELECTOR.HQL: select e.warehouse.id as id, e.warehouse.searchKey || ' - ' || e.warehouse.name as completename from swa_permissions_warehouse e where @additional_filters_notorg@ and e.active=true
